ust a flu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f54827ff06425e3f57819e54af5d3d3fd3d6f02","tid":1930920,"uid":43469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:13:40.000Z","msg":"北京稱禁記者在港工作屬外交事務職權範圍<br />\n<br />\n外交部要求《紐約時報》、《華爾街日報》及《華盛頓郵報》年底前記者證到期的美籍記者，10日內交還記者證，今後亦不得在港澳從事記者工作。在北京，外交部發言人耿爽說，有關措施完全是對美國無理打壓中國媒體駐美機構的必要反制，而禁止記者在港澳工作，亦屬於北京對外交事務的職權範圍，又強調當前局面的起因及責任不在中方。對於美國表明所有選項都擺在桌上，耿爽亦重申所有選項都在中方面前，敦促美方摘下意識形態有色眼鏡，摒棄冷戰、零和博弈思維，多做有利中美互信合作的事，又強調中方不惹事，但亦不怕事，敦促美方立即停止對中國媒體的打壓，否則損失更大的將會是美方。<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-18 17:31:02<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EhWLEsv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEhWLEsv.gif&h=e2b53677&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6882d7202d7a0bc9902d3d35bab53f3ac681e62e","tid":1930920,"uid":7778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrDmXer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrDmXer.jpg&h=d6d91bed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uhTFtk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuhTFtk8.jpg&h=19bea04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水隊駛唔駛咁多好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e04e10090f4fcef9fe0f03f5f8a759efef5c1273","tid":1930920,"uid":22531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6882d7202d7a0bc9902d3d35bab53f3ac681e62e","tid":1930920,"uid":7778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UrDmXer.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUrDmXer.jpg&h=d6d91bed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uhTFtk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuhTFtk8.jpg&h=19bea04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水隊駛唔駛咁多好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"rep